argparse
--------

-> see tag-count-2.py

import argparse

Simpler argument parsing! Handles things like:
- error handling
- help message i.e. -h and --help
- options and arguments being mixed (e.g. ls dir1 -l dir2)
- using -- to stop argument parsing (e.g. rm -- -dash to remove a file called "-dash")

See help(argparse) or https://docs.python.org/3/library/argparse.html
